{"tid":1182177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港70年代　風摩日本　現在都還有歌迷　日本人唱洋紫荊","createTime":"2019-06-02T04:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T05:53:15.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"43ecdf80978f1a9307c2ac45ae52e67cb90db845","tid":1182177,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:05:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/半斤八兩_(電影)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh%2F%E5%8D%8A%E6%96%A4%E5%85%AB%E5%85%A9_%28%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%29&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=43b7703e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/半斤八兩_(電影)</a><br />\n<br />\n《半斤八兩》是1976年香港賣座冠軍電影，首輪公映取得港幣800萬成績而打破票房開阜紀錄。1979年，《半斤八兩》在日本創下10億日元票房奇跡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.samhuifanclub.com/Story/menu2(2).html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.samhuifanclub.com%2FStory%2Fmenu2%282%29.html&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=04a23c6d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.samhuifanclub.com/Story/menu2(2).html</a><br />\n<br />\n四月「半斤八兩」在日上映，掀起一片Mr. Boo熱潮，而該唱片更於日本在三星期內售出超過五十萭張，曾打入日本流行榜，當地亦出現日文的「半斤 八兩」，五月Sam赴日宣傳「賣身契」。<br />\n<br />\n六月十七日，Sam以首位香港代表歌手，參加第八屆「東京音樂節」，以 「You Make Me Shine」獲TBS獎，無線曾以衛星直接轉播。 <br />\n<br />\n自「半斤八兩」後，Sam在日的聲名漸升，九月Sam再赴日替當地拍攝電視特輯，鬼馬雙星新版本也在日本上映，而日本著名電影雜誌 Screen十月更以 Sam為海報人物，同時日本的電視台、電台及報章亦組成記者團，於二十日來港為許氏兄弟作專訪。<br />\n<br />\n八一年三月二十一日在大球場舉行的兩場演唱會，世界各地歌迷來港為Sam打氣，由於Sam在日極受歡迎，日本歌迷特組團親臨欣賞，Sam因看見一班熱情歌迷，提著橫額，不斷高聲歡呼， 在唱「這一曲送給您」時，被感動至洒下英雄淚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港は九龍の夜景と許冠傑の洋紫荊おもちゃくん<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=roppopnGrgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DroppopnGrgc&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=e25021e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=roppopnGrgc</a><br />\n<br />\n日本人唱 杯酒當歌 卡啦OK 日文片假名標音<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OCpYr-UwJWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOCpYr-UwJWk&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=061cf19f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OCpYr-UwJWk</a><br />\n<br />\n日本人唱 宇宙無限 日語版 卡啦OK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OF6VKXNUcec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOF6VKXNUcec&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=72531fd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OF6VKXNUcec</a><br />\n<br />\n日本人唱 滄海一聲笑 日語版 卡啦OK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KmnxTO7NIO4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKmnxTO7NIO4&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=c70da528\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KmnxTO7NIO4</a><br />\n<br />\n日本人唱 悪漢探偵 即係《最佳拍檔》 左邊件衫印有許冠傑嘜頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QJZr2wQlyQ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQJZr2wQlyQ8&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=8cac3319\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QJZr2wQlyQ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實許冠傑o既歌好多日語版可以Google到<br />\n仲有英語版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9tq6SxpbrNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9tq6SxpbrNU&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI28HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=e37028b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9tq6SxpbrNU</a>"},{"pid":"5d49d172738ff5956667389c1695f56fb6d712ff","tid":1182177,"uid":191815,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:14:42.000Z","msg":"打夠J未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef1f1a580dbd7ee246281249fae9d59197b1666","tid":1182177,"uid":194785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"2019啦<br />\n準備好6月9日好過啦"},{"pid":"0433128c